collectible.description:
For us at AM2000, JetPacks are the ultimate expression of personal freedom. Buckle In. Throttle Up.
And you’re off. Reach high floors faster and with more maneuverability.
Military grade engine, 10,000 feet maximum altitude and 30 miles per hour forward flight speed, Lifetime Battery, Water Resistant (do not use under the rain).
